zzo）</a>为粉丝们提供了她新音乐时代的预览，并宣称她正在与即将发行的发行版中“真正地陷入困境”。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="917" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lizzo-live-in-london-a-glastonbury-headline-slot-worthy-spectacle-3416829"><b>Lizzo Live在伦敦：Glastonbury头条新闻的奇观</b></a></li></ul><p>这位歌手于周五（2月14日）在Twitch上直播，在那里她介绍了自己哭泣的片段。当她的眼泪慢慢地散发出笑声时，Lizzo结束了剪辑，凝视着镜头，而日期“ 2月28日”在屏幕上闪烁。</p><p>她说：“我想向你们介绍，这是新时代的最新内容。” “过去两年来我从事新音乐。我花了一些时间，做对了”。</p><p>她继续说：“新时代今天开始。” “我真的要插科打throt。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGCOUHSvJZL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36