 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据周五（2月14日2月14日）提交的法院文件，一名妇女声称她在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a>和Sean“ Diddy” Combs 13岁时受到性侵犯，自愿撤回诉讼。</p><p>该诉讼<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/with-legal-jay-z-accused-of-raping-13-year-old-girl-with-diddy-lawsuit-reveals-3820201">最初是由Jane Doe于12月提起的</a>，Jane Doe声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/with-legal-jay-z-accused-of-raping-13-year-old-girl-with-diddy-lawsuit-reveals-3820201">她在VMA派对上受到了两位艺术家的性侵犯</a>。</p><p>这位匿名指控者随后提交了<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/jay-z-sean-combs-accuser-drops-sexual-assault-lawsuit-1235264996/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>滚石</i></a>来获得的文件，告知法院她正在以偏见撤回投诉，这意味着她无法再提出。</p><p>梳子的律师<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-arrested-sexual-misconduct-allegations-3794341">被捕</a>，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-charged-with-sex-trafficking-racketeering-and-transporting-for-prostitution-3794598">指控犯有犯罪，包括去年9月的性贩运和敲诈勒索</a>，目前正在联邦监狱中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddys-sex-trafficking-trial-date-set-for-2025-3801704">等待审判</a>。 Combs一直<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-charged-with-sex-trafficking-racketeering-and-transporting-for-prostitution-3794598">否认所有针对他提出的指控</a>。</p><p>罗克民族（Roc Nation）的创始人杰伊·Z（Jay-Z）出生于肖恩·卡特（Shawn Carter），在12月的一项修正的投诉中命名他后，不断否认他的“令人发指的”指控，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jay-z-hits-out-at-rape-accusers-lawyer-for-getting-basic-facts-wrong-3833305">曾因“错误地犯错事实”而对他的原告律师袭击</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3820380" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3820380" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3820380" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-z-2024@2000x1270.jpg" alt="杰伊·Z（Jay Z）在2024年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-z-2024@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jay-z-2024@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://ww